OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fgradually easing through the evening.
OL,7,FBecoming largely dry with some lengthy
OL,8,Fclear spells developing, especially
OL,9,Finland. Turning chilly, with local
OL,10,Ffrost in sheltered rural spots. Breezy
OL,11,Falong coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,14,Fbe largely dry with variable cloud and
OL,15,Fbright or sunny spells. Breezy with a
OL,16,Ffew light showers along the coasts.
OL,17,FFeeling cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
