OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FAnother
OL,6,Fchilly start on Saturday, otherwise
OL,7,Flargely dry with sunny spells. A band
OL,8,Fof rain moves east on Sunday, breaking
OL,9,Fup into showers, locally heavy. Drier
OL,10,Fand warmer on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
